                        <div class="section__sidebar">
                            <h3 class="section__title section__title--left h4">
                                Cloud Infrastructure
                            </h3>
                            <p class="section__desc p-4">
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Your data is always safe
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                By distributing server data across redundant cloud-based servers, your data is
                                always
                                protected against failure and downtime.
                            </span>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Enhanced Reliability
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                Access your files and databases up to 300% faster with our enterprise-grade SSD
                                drives.
                                Because solid-state drives are more efficient in handling read/write operations,
                                SSDs are
                                more capable of handling peak use times.
                            </span>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Account Isolation
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                Our shared hosting servers use CageFS, a virtual filesystem that completely
                                isolates each
                                user's data and processes in a CloudLinux dedicated virtual environment.
                            </span>
                        </div>
