                        <div class="section__sidebar">
                            <h3 class="section__title section__title--left h4">
                                24/7 Monitoring
                            </h3>
                            <p class="section__desc p-4">
                            </p>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Server health monitored in realtime
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                Complete peace of mind with around-the-clock proactive server monitoring. Our team
                                of
                                highly experienced system administrators is watching over our platform 24/7 and
                                ready to
                                act when any issue is detected.
                            </span>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Website Monitoring
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                To ensure your website is available to your visitors, we perform website
                                accessibility checks
                                every 60 seconds from multiple independent locations over the globe.
                            </span>
                            <h4 class="section__subtitle h6">
                                Service Monitoring
                            </h4>
                            <span class="section__desc p-4">
                                From HTTPD to MySQL, Mail, FTP, and many more, we monitor every essential service
                                at
                                the server-side. In case any issue arises, our systems administrators will take
                                action right
                                away.
                            </span>
                        </div>
